        <item>
        <title>Myfirstblog</title>
        <link>https://hikaritsai.github.io/p/myfirstblog/</link>
        <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 00:29:01 +0800</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://hikaritsai.github.io/p/myfirstblog/</guid>
        <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;关于这个网站的一切&#34;&gt;关于这个网站的一切
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;这是本站的第一篇正式文章，也是我搭建这个个人网站、开启持续记录与分享的起点。搭建这个网站，核心初衷是告别零散的碎片化记录，系统化梳理个人成长与所思所感。后续本站将长期稳定更新三大核心内容板块，内容兼顾专业性与生活化，力求多元且扎实。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;其一，浅谈感兴趣的技术。我会更新一些感兴趣的技术领域的动态与原理，，结合自身学习与实践经历，输出一些个人技术浅谈、问题复盘与学习心得，希望能为同样深耕技术、热爱学习的读者提供参考。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;其二，日常生活记录与感悟。我会不定期记录生活中的所见所闻、所思所感，分享日常成长、生活感悟、细碎美好与人生思考，记录个人的生活轨迹。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;其三，游戏内容赏析与探讨。我会分享一些好玩的游戏体验和玩法解析，同时谈谈我的一些想法。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;感谢每一位偶然到访、驻足关注的读者。这个博客不仅是我的个人成长自留地，也希望能成为与大家交流学习、互通思想的小平台。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;期待与各位在此相遇、交流、共同成长，也欢迎大家持续关注本站，多多指正交流。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​																									谢谢大家。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;all-about-this-website&#34;&gt;All about this website
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is the first official article on this website, and it marks the beginning of my establishing my personal website and starting to continuously record and share. The main purpose of building this website is to bid farewell to scattered and fragmented records and to systematically organize my personal growth and thoughts and feelings. In the future, this website will regularly and stably update three core content sections. The content will balance professionalism and life-orientedness, aiming to be diverse and solid.
Firstly, a brief discussion on interesting technologies. I will observe the developments and principles in some technology-related fields, and combine my own learning and practical experiences to present some personal insights on technology, problem reviews, and learning reflections. I hope this can provide reference for readers who are deeply engaged in technology and passionate about learning.
Secondly, daily life records and reflections. I will periodically document what I observe and experience, my thoughts and feelings, sharing my daily growth, life insights, small joys and life reflections, and recording my personal life journey.
Thirdly, analysis and discussion of game content. I will share some enjoyable gaming experiences and gameplay explanations, and also express some of my thoughts.
Thank you to every reader who happened to visit and paid attention. This blog is not only my personal space for personal growth, but also I hope it can serve as a small platform for us to communicate, learn from each other and exchange ideas.
I am looking forward to meeting, communicating and growing together with all of you here. We also welcome everyone to keep following this website and offer us your valuable feedback and suggestions.
Thank you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hikaritsai.github.io/p/myfirstblog/index/Hikari.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1080&#34;
	height=&#34;1080&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hikaritsai.github.io/p/myfirstblog/index/Hikari_hu13575524403782386062.png 480w, https://hikaritsai.github.io/p/myfirstblog/index/Hikari_hu17654657305954150375.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;100&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;240px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
        <item>
        <title>Chinese Test</title>
        <link>https://hikaritsai.github.io/p/test-chinese/</link>
        <pubDate>Wed, 09 Sep 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
